%% Advanced showcase: nested subgraphs, edges-to-subgraph, every
%% node shape, <br/> labels, custom colors, fan-out, all link types.
flowchart TD
    Dev[/"Developer<br/>git push"/]:::human --> CI

    subgraph CI [CI/CD Pipeline]
        direction LR
        Build[[Build & Test]] --> Scan{{Security<br/>scan}}
        Scan -->|pass| Reg[(Artifact<br/>Registry)]
        Scan -.->|fail| Dev
    end

    Reg --> Platform

    subgraph Platform [Production Platform]
        Gate(API Gateway) --> Auth & Cache
        Auth[[Auth<br/>service]] --> Users[(Users DB)]
        Cache[(Redis)] --> Gate

        subgraph Workers [Async Workers]
            direction LR
            Q[(Job Queue)] --> W1[Worker 1]
            Q --> W2[Worker 2]
            W1 --> W1
        end
        Gate ==> Q
        W1 & W2 --> Users
    end

    Platform --> Mon{{Healthy?}}
    Mon -->|yes| Done(((Live)))
    Mon -->|no| Rollback[\Rollback\]
    Rollback --> Platform
    Users ~~~ Mon

    classDef human fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#f08c00,stroke-width:2px
    classDef danger fill:#ffe3e3,stroke:#e03131,color:#c92a2a
    Rollback:::danger
    style Done fill:#d3f9d8,stroke:#2b8a3e,stroke-width:3px
